headline: Weyerhaeuser: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: SEATTLE (AP) — Weyerhaeuser Co. (WY) on Thursday reported second-quarter net income of $87 million. The Seattle-based company said it had profit of 12 cents per share. The results beat Wall Street expectations.
